 University\">{{cite journal|url=https://archive.org/stream/universityofpitt821univ#page/4/mode/2up|title=The Celebration of the One Hundred and Twenty-Fifth Anniversary: History of the University|volume=8|issue=21|journal=University of Pittsburgh Bulletin|date=November 1, 1912|pages=4\u20135|accessdate=January 20, 2010}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Complete List: The Top 100 Global Universities\">{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14321230/site/newsweek/print/1/displaymode/1098/|title=The Complete List: The Top 100 Global Universities|work=Newsweek|date=August 10, 2006|accessdate=June 18, 2007 |url-status=dead|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070403020728/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14321230/site/newsweek/print/1/displaymode/1098/ |archivedate = April 3, 2007}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Nationality Rooms - rooms in planning\">{{cite web|url=http://www.pitt.edu/~natrooms/pages/rooms_in_planning.html |title=The Nationality Rooms \u2013 rooms in planning |publisher=Pitt.edu |accessdate=September 13, 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Pitt: The Story of the University of Pittsburgh 1787\u201319873\">{{cite web|url=http://www.originalmag.com/|title=The Original|accessdate=February 27, 2009}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Owl\">{{cite web|url=http://digital.library.pitt.edu/cgi-bin/t/text/pageviewer-idx?c=pittyearbooks;idno=1909e49702;seq=23|title=The Owl|page=10|date=1909|publisher=Western University of Pennsylvania|accessdate=April 28, 2008}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Panther\">{{cite web|url=http://pittsburghpanthers.cstv.com/trads/pitt-trads-mascot.html|title=The Panther|publisher=Pittsburgh Panthers|accessdate=April 28, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080408223749/http://pittsburghpanthers.cstv.com/trads/pitt-trads-mascot.html|archive-date=April 8, 2008|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Pymatuning Laboratory of Ecology\">{{cite web|url=http://www.pitt.edu/~biohome/Dept/Frame/pymatuninglabs.htm|title=The Pymatuning Laboratory of Ec